title: Pro-Government Protest: Groups Gather In Abuja
text:
Pro-Government Protest: Groups Gather In Abuja   
Another group of protesters who say they are in support of President Muhammadu Buhari, have gathered at the Unity Park, in the Federal Capital Territory (FCT), Abuja. 
Supporters were seen carrying placards with inscriptions such as: ”Nigerians support you sir, “your Government is a good government”. 
This protest apparently, is to counter the anti-Buhari demonstration which is also taking place at the Unity Park. 
So far, the conduct of the protesters on both sides have been peaceful but it is not clear if that would remain the case as procession across the city progresses. More on Local
